        .panel-footer
          button.btn.btn-danger.btn-lg.btn-block.error-submit(type="button", data-dismiss="modal") throw error

    script(type="text/template", id="number-template")
      h3.text-center <%= key %>
      p.description <%= description %>
      hr
      form.form-horizontal.number-form(role="form")
        fieldset
          .form-group
            input.form-control.floating-label.input-lg.number-value(type="number", placeholder!='<%= example %>', data-hint='you must put number')
            button.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.btn-block.return-submit(type="submit") submit
      hr
      a.btn.btn-warning.error-button throw error
      .error.fade.panel.panel-default
        .panel-body
          p.description エラーの理由を文字列で入力するか、選択肢から選んでください
